solution.p:
(a) The y coordinates of the constructive interference maxima are

	\amp m = 0:\ \ y=0 
	\amp m = \pm 1:\ \ y= \pm 21\text{ cm}
	\amp m = \pm 2:\ \ y= \pm 42\text{ cm}

(b) The y coordinates of the destructive interference are

	\amp m^\prime = \pm 1:\ \ y= \pm 10.5\text{ cm}
	\amp m = \pm 2:\ \ y= \pm 31.5\text{ cm}
